<view class="license-page">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">© 呆呆角</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section summary-section">
    <view class="body-copy">
      <text>呆呆角 基于 </text>
      <text class="quiet-inline" bindtap="toggleOpenSource">Macify</text>
      <text> 改造；背景视频按 </text>
      <text class="quiet-inline" bindtap="toggleSources">公开素材</text>
      <text> 平台许可用于应用内背景体验。</text>
    </view>
    <text class="quiet-note">素材版权归原作者或相应权利人所有；呆呆角 不声明拥有这些素材版权，也不提供素材下载、转售或独立素材库分发。</text>

    <view class="detail-panel" wx:if="{{isOpenSourceExpanded}}">
      <text class="detail-title">{{openSourceNotice.name}}</text>
      <text class="detail-line">{{openSourceNotice.license}} · {{openSourceNotice.copyright}}</text>
      <text class="detail-line">原作者：{{openSourceNotice.authors}}</text>
      <text class="detail-note">{{openSourceNotice.note}}</text>
    </view>

    <view class="detail-panel source-panel" wx:if="{{isSourcesExpanded}}">
      <view class="platform-entry" wx:for="{{platformSummaries}}" wx:key="name">
        <view class="source-row" data-name="{{item.name}}" bindtap="togglePlatform">
          <text class="source-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="source-count">{{item.videoCount}} 条</text>
        </view>

        <view class="platform-detail" wx:if="{{item.expanded}}">
          <text class="detail-line">{{item.license}}</text>
          <text class="detail-note">{{item.note}}</text>
          <view class="video-list">
            <view class="video-entry" wx:for="{{item.videos}}" wx:for-item="video" wx:key="id">
              <view class="video-row" data-platform="{{item.name}}" data-id="{{video.id}}" bindtap="toggleVideo">
                <text class="item-title">{{video.title}}</text>
              </view>

              <view class="video-detail" wx:if="{{video.expanded}}">
                <text class="detail-line" wx:if="{{video.location}}">地点：{{video.location}}</text>
                <text class="detail-line">来源：{{video.sourceName}} / {{video.attribution}}</text>
                <text class="detail-line">许可证：{{video.license}}</text>
                <text class="detail-line" wx:if="{{video.sourceResolution || video.duration}}">规格：{{video.sourceResolution}} {{video.duration}}</text>
                <text class="detail-note" wx:if="{{video.licenseNotes}}">{{video.licenseNotes}}</text>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
